# MEDHAVARDHAN Website

## About The Project

This is the front page for the MEDHAVARDHAN educational platform. It features a modern and futuristic design where students can prepare for various competitive exams like JEE, NATA, UCEED, and general competitions.

## Features

*   Modern and futuristic design
*   Fully responsive layout that works on all screen sizes
*   A dedicated hamburger menu for mobile navigation
*   Separate sections for Features, Courses, and Quiz Leagues

## Technology Used

*   HTML5
*   CSS3
*   JavaScript

## How to View

To view the website, open the `index.html` file located in this folder in any web browser.

## Color Theme

The website uses the following color palette:

*   #5e7f79
*   #d1dedc
*   #101417
*   #181e22
*   #4a6b67
*   #20272c
*   #cdd7d6
